        taskDueDate - Due date for task
        taskId - Tasks id
        userId - Id of the tasks user
        timeSpent - Amount of time user has worked on this task
        estimatedCompletionTime - How much time this task is estimated to take
        startDate - When the task was started, defaults to day the task is created
        completed - Boolean value of whether the task is completed
